snippet.title: Maria Cerneanu
snippet.description: A good trailer can recommend a movie. Are movies art or entertainment? Are films an art form out of reach for the general public? These are questions that we will answer ourselves, each and every one, over some years. This is a channel dedicated to the most interesting movie trailers. Most beautiful and inspirational movies ever made shall be represented in a particular list!
